    "title": "OpenSARToolkit (OST) by ESA-PhiLab",
    "description": "The Open SAR Toolkit (OST) was initially developed at the Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (FAO). It has now been completely re-factored and transferred into a simpler and less-dependency rich python3 version. OST lowers the entry barrier for pre-processing of Sentinel-1 data. OST supports the production of ARD products, either Radiometrically Terrain Corrected (RTC) products or Geometrically Terrain Corrected (GTC) products, along with option to automate the generation of small to large-scale Sentinel-1 time-series and timescan data.",
